data.description: Wonderful 4-bedroom home in coveted Stockwell Place. One-story, open floor plan with a thoughtful layout. Tall ceilings and many windows welcome beautiful natural light throughout. Pretty foyer with customized Italian travertine floor detail. Charming arched doorways. Expansive great room with gas fireplace and a sleek stone surround. The kitchen features ample storage, granite countertops, tile backsplash, an island with seating plus an additional dining area. The door in the great room and kitchen goes out to the covered patio, perfect for entertaining. The backyard is like a private retreat and backs up to the woods. The property line extends past the tree line. Spacious primary suite with vaulted ceiling, separate from other bedrooms. Great closets throughout. Pretty brick exterior facade. 2-car attached garage. Laundry room with great storage and a sink right off the garage. The seller is willing to provide a carpet allowance. Roof and HVAC are only two years old. A Must See!
